{"tid":868322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為5顆免費雞蛋排隊6小時 中國老人等到尿失禁","createTime":"2018-10-19T11:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T12:21:14.000Z","uid":75969,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a79f7688cfff2535a702a0c3af8d037becbe55d1","tid":868322,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php57VIV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php57VIV5.jpg&h=fb325512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國河南省鄭州有一群老人，15日為了商家免費送雞蛋的活動，不惜凌晨排隊，還有人等太久，不慎尿失禁。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，當地有家藥房考量到消費者主要是老人，於是祭出開幕當天，分上下午場各前80位民眾，每人可免費拿到5顆雞蛋的宣傳活動。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，活動當日吸引附近上百名老人排隊，且大多數人自備椅凳；據悉，上午場有老人為了這5顆免費雞蛋，自凌晨4點就開始排隊等候，足足等了6小時，更有位排隊婦人尿急找不到廁所，因此當眾不慎尿失禁。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友對此揶揄，「愛貪小便宜的人」、「雞蛋3塊錢的事，身體不適掛號費30塊」、「褲子尿了回去洗洗就好了，5個雞蛋多實惠」；但也有人對排隊老人的行為表示，「苦日子過慣了」、「他們不缺雞蛋，缺的是陪伴。」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2584273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2584273&d=WXSjg9b4xvSczAxs9sVyRYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a6ef8951\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2584273&h=0aee9a7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2584273</a><br />\n<br />\n強國廢老真係貪小便宜嘅極致<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724a2de6f71f231ecf7abe694c61cc368d4e335b","tid":868322,"uid":34223,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"都係痾落地啫 扮乜"},{"pid":"5c59597b15cfe9188734a4a199fa384e57305a59","tid":868322,"uid":29880,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:13:51.000Z","msg":"每逢見到廢老排隊<br />\n就知有免費野派"},{"pid":"40455d08a9237e2a16e2cdd339261d31e3c88095","tid":868322,"uid":36551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"低成本撚鳩班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7c1a19755f0f544e7664539cd02be1189878b8","tid":868322,"uid":48521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"拎五百出黎可以撚一百個人"},{"pid":"e74f00222dd4b8636b2adab37f90f9a83ef5c3a9","tid":868322,"uid":52009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"「他們不缺雞蛋，缺的是陪伴。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c50a6bf3fb1de520c4ab9ee35150d1eb8c5d80","tid":868322,"uid":86898,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/column/images/stories/73/2015/12/1209godiva02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.etnet.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2Fimages%2Fstories%2F73%2F2015%2F12%2F1209godiva02.jpg&h=f2da0d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b18c266dcf220e253cf6ead8ef36d3647291d4a","tid":868322,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:23:45.000Z","msg":"好撚可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17b03c1f3b9968d625b0252551ee2a35cc59b07","tid":868322,"uid":72647,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:31:58.000Z","msg":"班老野好窮，副身家用一蚊少一蚊。 平時又得閒，所以咪去排隊囉"},{"pid":"e72c26be3bf20acd38574f6096156cd0fc995ae9","tid":868322,"uid":56459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"香港排報紙"},{"pid":"51af30319397448839ad914944e37e9c9064482e","tid":868